				<li><a class="body-link" href="http://www.woodsbeer.com" target="_blank">Woods Beer Company</a> &mdash; Super fun brewery with lots of unique beers. This guy really pushes the limits of flavors. Woods Cervecer√≠a is the original location and you can get a crowler to go and drink it in Dolores Park! </li>
